room_title: Escape room "The Dorm Rooms" by Ace of Escape in Tucson
room_description: You choose to help either your U of A or ASU classmate in a bind. You'll need to become the University mascot for tonight's game in 1 hour, but security is top notch around the mascot costume. Your buddy left you some information to get started, but that's about it so you search through his dorm room decoding clues all the while getting in the mood for the big game!
